# Crontabs
### 'export DISPLAY=:0.0' is for making notifications with notify-send work

## Uppdate RSS feed
*/45 */4 * * *		export DISPLAY=:0.0; sh /home/mqx/.local/bin/cron/newsup

## Activate light
@reboot			/home/mqx/.local/bin/light_activation

## Activate ProtonVPN
@reboot			/usr/bin/sleep 12; export DISPLAY=:0.0; sh /home/mqx/.local/bin/proton_vpn

## Activate calcurse reminders
@reboot			/usr/bin/sleep 300; export DISPLAY=:0.0; sh /home/mqx/.local/bin/calcurse_reminders || /usr/bin/notify-send "❗ Error opening calcurse_reminders ❗"

## Update packages
@reboot			/usr/bin/sleep 120; export DISPLAY=:0.0; sh /home/mqx/.local/bin/cron/checkup
